@0=~"I heard there is a guest professor in the Hall, Mawu. Do you know where she is?"~
@1=~"Oh, her? She should be in one of the lecture halls. When she's not lecturing she loves to listen in on others. Look for a lady with a darker complexion, bright blonde hair and a green dress."~
@2=~"Thank you. I have some other questions."~
@3=~"Thank you. That will be all for now."~
